            <V n="text" t="variation">
              <U n="variation">
                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0x47C2D59D<!--String: "I'm pretty close with my sibling, Laxmi, but I confess that I'm closest to Toshie. She's the Storyteller over in Jellyfish Junction. When we were kids and we'd hang out, I felt like she always got me. She'd tell me stories about great adventurers from the past in Gibbi Point and say: "Someday, Raheel, you'll be a great adventurer, too." She's so kind."--></T>
                  <T>0x56DD9AD2<!--String: "I spend a lot of my time hanging around the Old Firewatch Tower, cuz my favorite fishing spot is right nearby, and I feel like it gives me a bird's eye view of the neighborhood (or should I say...Plumbird's eye view?). I swear I've seen that weird little kid Buddy Scoop going up there sometimes. You don't think he lives there, do you?"--></T>
                  <T>0x91C74F77<!--String: "I saw that Peculiar Plumbird critter running over to the 'Round the Fire Festival once. I thought she was supposed to be a bit reclusive like me? Maybe she just can't resist the allure of a good toasted marshmallow and a chance to tell scary cryptid stories. "--></T>
                </L>
              </U>
            </V>
            <V n="title" t="enabled">
